trans-unit.source: Provides a user interface for representing and editing the values the Windows Workflow Foundation types in an object browser associated with a workflow designer.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder et brukergrensesnitt for som representerer og redigere verdiene Windows arbeidsflyten Foundation typene i en nettleser for objektet som er tilknyttet en arbeidsflyt designer.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] This class allows users to open object browsers associated with any workflow designer and view all types and members that reside in the Windows Workflow Foundation namespaces.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Denne klassen kan brukere å åpne objektet nettlesere som er tilknyttet en arbeidsflyt-designeren og vise alle typer og medlemmer som ligger i Windows-arbeidsflyten Foundation-navneområder.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Edits the value of the specified object using the editor style indicated by <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.GetEditStyle*>.
trans-unit.target: Redigerer verdien for det angitte objektet ved hjelp av redigeringsprogrammet stil som er angitt av <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.GetEditStyle*>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.GetEditStyle*>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som kan brukes til å få ytterligere kontekstinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.IServiceProvider> that the editor can use to obtain services.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.IServiceProvider>at redigeringsprogrammet kan bruke til å hente services.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: The new value of the object.
typeDescriptorContext or serviceProvider contains a null reference ( in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: typeDescriptorContexteller serviceProvider inneholder en nullreferanse ( i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.IServiceProvider.GetService*> returns a null reference (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref>) when it attempts to obtain the type provider.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.IServiceProvider.GetService*>Returnerer en nullreferanse (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref>) når den prøver å hente typen leverandøren.</xref:System.IServiceProvider.GetService*>

trans-unit.source: Returns the editor style used by the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.EditValue*> method.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer redigeringsprogrammet stilen brukes av den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.EditValue*>metoden.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.EditValue*>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som kan brukes til å få ytterligere kontekstinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref> value that indicates the style of editor used by <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.EditValue*>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"> </xref> verdi som angir stilen på redigeringsprogrammet brukes av <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.EditValue*>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.EditValue*>

trans-unit.source: Unless overridden by an inheriting class, this method returns <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Med mindre overstyres med en arvede klasse, metoden returnerer <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"> </xref>.
